{"tid":2106310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［HKTVmall]員工可在家工作 不過需承諾鈴聲三聲之內接聽電話及假日不可與朋友飯聚","createTime":"2020-07-13T09:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T13:23:25.000Z","uid":22556,"like":78,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"4644fbab588bd8d3d8bcb3059201706ca1ee67fd","tid":2106310,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"香港電視（1137）今日發出內部電郵，指為保障同事及社區，減低感染及傳染機會，並同時維持集團電子商貿的業務運作及客戶的服務，集團現提供100% 「在家工作」計劃，但條件十分嚴謹。<br />\n<br />\n員工亦需承諾，星期六、日及公眾假期 : 只可外出購買必需品，亦不可外出與朋友飯聚、行街、行山、 娛樂及消遣活動如戲院睇戲、商場購物等。需要將手提電話設定為響鬧模式，並於電話鈴聲三聲之內接聽電話、並需要將公司直線電話轉駁至其手提電話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200713&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=61162778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200713%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D61162778&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxKC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=b120d7e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200713%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D61162778&h=dde83df2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200713&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=61162778</a>"},{"pid":"8de128244767518f616afe302ad5fe7714911b6d","tid":2106310,"uid":3513,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:03:42.000Z","msg":"今日仲有堆人話fc左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f417c7aac24aca05b82d674944c49e9a308de8","tid":2106310,"uid":25260,"like":10,"dislike":27,"score":-17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"假日做乜都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc32c9c1e96a936dc9867384aff077c19dfa7c7","tid":2106310,"uid":2583,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:05:58.000Z","msg":"冇得行山了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm